            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>陶氏(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DOW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DOW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DOW-US</a>)截至台北時間12日21:30股價上漲1.72美元，報36.09美元，漲幅5%，成交量748,663（股），盤中最高價36.10美元、最低價35.51美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.27%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.82%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.87%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.77%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>陶氏(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DOW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DOW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DOW-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+6.28%</li> <li>近 1 月：+1.09%</li> <li>近 3 月：+39.83%</li> <li>近 6 月：+44.23%</li> <li>今年以來：+47.01%</li></ul></section></main>",
